snippet: On his organization’s 10th anniversary, he vowed to release “significant material” about a range of issues, including the U.S. election....
abstract: WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange plans to release 'significant material' on several subjects, including United States election, over 10 weeks; refutes idea that election-related material, set for release before Nov 8, is meant to harm Hillary Clinton and vows to continue providing platform for classified document leaks.
lead_paragraph: On his organization’s 10th anniversary, he vowed to release “significant material” about a range of issues, including the U.S. election.

headline.main: Julian Assange, WikiLeaks Founder, Promises Raft of Revelations
headline.print_headline: Assange Sets New Schedule of Disclosures
